      "published_date": "2025-11-19T00:00:00.000Z",
      "text": "California Independent System Operator Corporation\nFifth Replacement Electronic Tariff\nNovember 19, 2025\nSection 8\nTable of Contents\n8. Ancillary Services ........................................................................................................... 3\n8.1 Scope ....................................................................................................................... 3\n8.2 Ancillary Services Standards ........................................................................................ 4\n8.2.1 Determination of Ancillary Service Standards .............................................................. 4\n8.2.2 Time-Frame for Revising Ancillary Service Standards................................................... 4\n8.2.3 Quantities of Ancillary Services Required; Use of AS Regions........................................ 5\n8.3 Procurement; Certification and Testing; Contracting Period ............................................... 9\n8.3.1 Procurement of Ancillary",
