ectric Reliability Council (NERC) Criteria to the extent they\nare applicable to the ISO Controlled Grid. (b) The ISO may adjust the Ancillary Services standards\ntemporarily to take into account, among other things,  ...    ASRP 3 ANCILLARY SERVICE OBLIGATIONS FOR SCHEDULING\nCOORDINATORS\nASRP 3.1 Ancillary Service Obligations The ISO shall assign to each Scheduling Coordinator a share of the ISO’s total Regulation, Spinning Reserve, Non-Spinning Reserve and Replacement Reserve requirements. The ISO will calculate the  ...    “obligation”) in accordance with the standards set forth in the\nASRP.\nASRP 3.2 Right to Self Provide  ...    its Regulation and Reserve obligation within each Zone.\nASRP 4 REGULATION STANDARDS  ...    The ISO needs sufficient Gener"
